room_title: Escape room "Spy Room" by Xcape Room Fresno in Fresno
room_address: 3475 W Shaw Ave Suite #103 Fresno, California 93711
room_description: Greetings, Agents! Our outpost has been compromised by a double agent, and it is your job to catch him! The man we suspect of committing the treason is named Thomas Barrett. Gather your team to investigate a recently discovered hidden basement located near his property. You have a time window of sixty minutes before he returns.
